&lt;p&gt;We are looking to employ a CBT therapist to work into the Sheffield CAMHS team. The person will be registered with the HCPC and be an accreditated CBT therapist with the BABCP.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The CAMHS team is a diverse and lively team, with a range of therapists, nurses, psychologists and psychiatrists working into the team. There is a lot of support in the team from other CBT therapists and appropriate supervision will be offered in order to ensure that the post holder can retain their accredidation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please do get in touch to discuss the post further as we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
